description: Commands : ##### Create an event > !CreateEvent NameofTheEvent Date Hours ##### Delete an event > !DeleteEvent NameofTheEvent ##### Join an event as accepted with a role (Like Dps,Tank,Heal) > !Accepted NameofTheEvent Role ##### Join an event as undecided with a role (Like Dps,Tank,Heal) > !Undecided NameofTheEvent Role ##### Show all the information of the event(Name,Date,hours,PlayersAccepted and they're role , player undecided and they're role) > !Read NameofTheEvent
